headline: FMCSA Revokes ROBINHOOD ELD, The Price Value Dilemma
summary: The removal of ROBINHOOD ELD from FMCSA's registered devices list underscores the importance of selecting reputable ELD vendors, as fleets now face a 60-day scramble to replace systems while managing driver frustration and operational disruption. The post FMCSA Revokes ROBINHOOD ELD, The Price Value Dilemma appeared first on FreightWaves.
